{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/how-this-topic-was-developed/declarations-of-interest/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"91e54862-93aa-5c58-820e-b47769d73d34","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 2dab21dc-ebb2-4e5d-a8c0-a7f30015cde8 --><h2>Declarations of interest</h2><!-- end field 2dab21dc-ebb2-4e5d-a8c0-a7f30015cde8 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item fa286ff7-6d25-4839-99fd-a7f30015bd73 --><!-- begin field 5107dde2-1061-4389-be29-a7f30015cde8 --><h2>Our policy</h2><!-- end field 5107dde2-1061-4389-be29-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- begin field ce27b6c4-b110-4106-8fef-a7f30015cde8 --><p>Clarity Informatics requests that all those involved in the writing and reviewing of topics, and those involved in the external review process to declare any competing interests. Signed copies are securely held by Clarity Informatics and are available on request with the permission of the individual. A copy of the declaration of interest form which participants are asked to complete annually is also available on request. A brief outline of the declarations of interest policy is described here and full details of the policy is available on the <a href=\"https://cks.clarity.co.uk/\" data-hyperlink-id=\"8080c632-053d-4210-a9db-a992002c869d\">Clarity Informatics website</a>. Declarations of interests of the authors are not routinely published, however competing interests of all those involved in the topic update or development are listed below. Competing interests include:</p><ul><li>Personal financial interests</li><li>Personal family interest</li><li>Personal non-financial interest</li><li>Non-personal financial gain or benefit</li></ul><p>Although particular attention is given to interests that could result in financial gains or losses for the individual, competing interests may also arise from academic competition or for political, personal, religious, and reputational reasons. An individual is not obliged to seek out knowledge of work done for, or on behalf of, the healthcare industry within the departments for which they are responsible if they would not normally expect to be informed.</p><!-- end field ce27b6c4-b110-4106-8fef-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- begin field 2d1a4ecf-8446-473d-bc6b-a7f30015cde8 --><h2>Who should declare competing interests?</h2><!-- end field 2d1a4ecf-8446-473d-bc6b-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- begin field a0d1e3d6-d54e-4295-9042-a7f30015cde8 --><p>Any individual (or organization) involved in developing, reviewing, or commenting on clinical content, particularly the recommendations should declare competing interests. This includes the authoring team members, expert advisers, external reviewers of draft topics, individuals providing feedback on published topics, and Editorial Steering Group members. Declarations of interest are completed annually for authoring team and editorial steering group members, and are completed at the start of the topic update and development process for external stakeholders.</p><!-- end field a0d1e3d6-d54e-4295-9042-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- begin field aaeebb1a-d4ac-4681-9280-a7f30015cde8 --><h2>Competing interests declared for this topic:</h2><!-- end field aaeebb1a-d4ac-4681-9280-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- begin field ada439e9-ab16-412d-9b79-a7f30015cde8 --><p>None.</p><!-- end field ada439e9-ab16-412d-9b79-a7f30015cde8 --><!-- end item fa286ff7-6d25-4839-99fd-a7f30015bd73 -->","topic":{"id":"b7a3c2c6-f067-5a2a-b5cb-565b52b08dc1","topicId":"b5c1d99b-f98a-4932-aced-7f81b69fb4ca","topicName":"Gingivitis and periodontitis","slug":"gingivitis-periodontitis","lastRevised":"Last revised in October 2018","chapters":[{"id":"cfb38419-7c7d-546b-8d5f-53e5d90275c8","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"191a777c-922f-5a14-a229-027026e22c77","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"638e02dc-c117-5dc3-9aa2-51475ec65732","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"6b07dd54-bace-502f-9276-99b0dcadf72c","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"7c3133f1-1499-5e4d-bde7-4f9ef73dffb1","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"f07ed878-39d1-558e-bdcf-a3534fbe9f72","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"fce21703-845c-5ce9-9585-48763e017d5e","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"691f6953-69ca-5faa-b66a-e823f1bee170","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"f8871332-adda-5da7-97ec-504b02f786b6","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"17f48184-7c27-5119-8501-763285466de0","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"f3ba2a3b-9abc-5b17-9b87-e9d0aeb47c16","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"c331f8e2-8a7c-55b8-b53a-529654d16bcb","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"ab65ace2-7dee-5a4f-b482-e3651b2a2297","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"d42e9a6f-6cc4-5fb1-954b-df84d1ede6d2","slug":"definition","fullItemName":"Definition"},{"id":"2710e428-c488-512b-88cf-a92c0ad2f06a","slug":"causes","fullItemName":"Causes"},{"id":"480011f9-df8c-5474-8906-cc1d841f5886","slug":"risk-factors","fullItemName":"Risk factors"},{"id":"fcc38926-22fe-5da1-bd3f-a0d4a6c7a435","slug":"prevalence","fullItemName":"Prevalence"},{"id":"c90bf0c2-4d5e-563f-b89e-9a4661169933","slug":"complications-prognosis","fullItemName":"Complications and prognosis"}]},{"id":"07bf77ad-d5e5-5c15-8d6e-ed41f1db4df3","fullItemName":"Diagnosis","slug":"diagnosis","subChapters":[{"id":"a808be6b-7265-53ab-87ef-2daf69d421a6","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},{"id":"d2528eb4